  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Spacetime)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 26 | <b>Successes:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 14 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 34</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, P</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>A withered wooden coffin springs forth from the ground within 15 ft of you. On your next turn, it opens, sending eight shadowy hands to make ranged touch attacks at a +10 bonus against the target. If at least five attacks hit, a larger hand flies out to make another touch attack at a +22 bonus, which will drag the target into the coffin if it hits.<br><br>Once it has caught a creature, the coffin sinks back into the ground. Each round, the creature takes 1d4 negative energy damage and must make a save to avoid taking 1 temporary Charisma damage.<br><br>If the target dies before it reaches 0 Charisma, the coffin surfaces and releases its corpse. If it reaches 0 Charisma before dying, it is completely healed of all damage caused by the technique and rises towards the surface, coming under your complete control for 1 hour per level.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
